# Remember to never publicly share your keystore.
# See https://flutter.dev/to/reference-keystore
key.properties
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks

# Intentionally tracked: a shared release keystore so every build (local and
# CI) signs identically and Android can update an installed app in place. This
# is a throwaway key for a personal, sideloaded app that is NOT published to
# the Play Store. If this app is ever published, generate a private keystore,
# move it to CI secrets, and delete these two lines.
!key.properties
!app/upload-keystore.jks
